  "texts": [
    "IntroductionSign language is a communication tool that deaf and dumb people use to convey their feelings, thoughts, desires etc.",
    "to the outside of their world.",
    "It has a nonverbal form of communication that uses hands, arm, head, facial gestures and body posture.",
    "According to the data of the world health organization in 2021, there are around 466 million people suffering from hearing loss around the world including 34 million children.",
    "It is estimated that this number will exceed 700 million by 2050 Word (Health Organization, 2021)."
